Subscription Charge Key: [Enter either ID or Number of the Subscription Charge you want to create this Revenue Schedule under.]
Revenue Schedule Date: [Enter a date in the YYYY-MM-DD format]
#Currency: [This is an informational field.  You can create an informational field by adding # in front of the column name.  We will not process any values for these informational fields.]
Revenue Schedule Amount: [Enter the amount for this Revenue Schedule.]
Recognized Revenue Accounting Code: [Enter the name of the Recognized Revenue Accounting Code.  This field is optional.  If this field is not entered, we will use the Recognized Revenue Accounting Code from the Subscription Charge.]
Deferred Revenue Accounting Code: [Enter the name of the Deferred Revenue Accounting Code.  This field is optional.  If this field is not entered, we will use the Deferred Revenue Accounting Code from the Subscription Charge.]
Revenue Schedule Notes: [Enter any notes you want to associate to the Revenue Schedule.  This field is optional.]
Revenue Schedule:rspicklist: [Enter the value for the custom field you have defined on the Revenue Schedule.  You can add more columns to include other custom fields.]
Revenue Schedule:rstext: [Enter the value for the custom field you have defined on the Revenue Schedule.  You can add more columns to include other custom fields.]
Revenue Event Type: [Enter either System ID or Label for a Revenue Event Type that describes the creation of this Revenue Schedule.]
Revenue Event:repicklist: [Enter the value for the custom field you have defined on the Revenue Event.  You can add more columns to include other custom fields.]
Revenue Event:retext: [Enter the value for the custom field you have defined on the Revenue Event.  You can add more columns to include other custom fields.]
Distribution Type: [Enter either 'Manual - fixed', 'Date Range - daily' or 'Date Range - monthly']
Recognition Start: [This is applicable when the Distribution Type is 'Date Range - daily'.  We will create Revenue Schedule distributing revenue daily between Recognition Start and Recognition End.  Please enter a date in the format of YYYY-MM-DD.]
Recognition End: [This is applicable when the Distribution Type is 'Date Range - daily'.  We will create Revenue Schedule distributing revenue daily between Recognition Start and Recognition End.  Please enter a date in the format of YYYY-MM-DD.]
Feb-2015: [This is applicable when the Distribution Type is 'Manual - fixed'.  Please put in how you want to distribute the revenue into each accounting period.]
